description: Aww, what a shame. I wonder if\nthe Majimun's got my soul now?
My dancing's all off beat today!\nI gotta eat some goya veggies\nand get back in high spirits!
There's Majimuns all over\nthe place! My head's getting\nall spinny!
There's always next time,\nso don't sweat it! Let's go\nfor a nice, refreshing swim!
That sure was embarrassing.\nHuh? Who said anything about\nmy swimsuit?
Doing great! Let's bring back\npeace to the ocean! A super fun\nsummer's waiting for us!
You can keep coming at me, but\nmy anima's going nowhere!\nAchoo! Oh no! I might have lost it!
Hiyasasa! ♪ Nothing like a\ngood dance after fighting to\nget all refreshed!
Huh? My swimsuit disappeared in\nthe middle of that fight. Do you\nknow where it is? Hey, don't leave!
I've got plenty left in the tank!\nNo Majimun or anything else is\ngonna take me down! ♪
My karate's the best in the world!\nI'm unstoppable when I've got the sun and ocean on my side!
